data.title: Music Producer Timbaland Reflects On His Life's Work
data.meta_description: For two decades now, Timothy Mosley, who goes by Timbaland, has been producing some of music's biggest stars.
data.text:
If you don't know Timbaland by name, you've certainly heard his music.

For two decades now, Timothy Mosley, who goes by Timbaland, has been producing some of music's biggest stars, including Missy Elliot, Jay-Z, Madonna and both of Justin Timberlake's solo albums.

Here & Now's Jeremy Hobson spoke with Mosley last November about his life, his new memoir "The Emperor of Sound" — which comes out in paperback this week — and why he considers himself a musical genius.

Hear our original conversation with Timbaland from November 2015
